{"tid":186780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【戀上強姦犯】俄女為「公園色魔」求情減刑︰他迫不得已才犯案","createTime":"2017-04-04T12:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T01:00:17.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"afbb98564d603a76c470e1c54cf71df0f6f455cb","tid":186780,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">【動畫●戀上強姦犯】俄女為「公園色魔」求情減刑︰他迫不得已才犯案<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170403/56512755\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170403%2F56512755&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=b2587fae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170403%2F56512755&h=e36e2502\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170403/56512755</a></div></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170402/large/1491118141_9c9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170402%2Flarge%2F1491118141_9c9b.jpg&h=198ac627&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯下諾夫哥羅德一名20歲強姦案受害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不但放低仇恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、寬恕了施襲者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，還為他的刑期上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，希望他獲得減刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。她坦言自己與對方互通書信後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，慢慢愛上他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n案發在三年前，女受害人放學走到巴士站途中，被一名男子扯着頭髮，拉到一個公園的草叢中。其後男子粗暴地把她強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 命有危險，故不敢反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。但她不是案中唯一受害人，還有五名女子在同一個公園遭該男子強姦，當中四名女子的年齡都是16至17歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n案件在當年頗為轟動，施襲者被稱為「公園色魔」，有婦女團體在公園遊行，呼籲女性夜間不要走到公園。「公園色魔」最後被捕，但由於保密原因，庭上只稱呼他為埃韋尼（Evgeny）。埃韋尼被判強姦罪成，入獄17年。<br />\n<br />\n審訊期間，女受害人每天都到庭，並與犯人欄內的埃韋尼交換書信。法庭職員指，女受害人起初「憤怒地」向埃韋尼遞上字條，埃韋尼之後會作出回覆。想不到女受害人自此與埃韋尼越走越近<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，她向當地一份小報指，她擅於觀察人，至今發現埃韋尼是迫不得已才犯案。「我知道埃韋尼是一個好人，他只是走霉運。」<br />\n<br />\n她說埃韋尼的媽媽當時生病，太太又不忠貞，所以埃韋尼借酒澆愁，「當天他強姦我，他看來心不在焉。他喝醉了，因此他不能控制自己」。埃韋尼事後寫信要求她原諒，兩人慢慢轉為談及關於自身的事情，加深雙方的了解。後來她更對埃韋尼產生情愫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但她稱埃韋尼只當她是好朋友。<br />\n<br />\n女受害人如今正為埃韋尼的刑期上訴，希望法官減刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"e551164b15265d0b215fdb06d54ef36a0b5ed99f","tid":186780,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"呢d女仔邊到搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85040428377265389234158a4303f633ad2e9065","tid":186780,"uid":38301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d女仔邊到搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法庭裡面"},{"pid":"ac0458da883df90c8db048803bf8a839fcbbd826","tid":186780,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:42:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d女仔邊到搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n青山"},{"pid":"7b5ff10bf8b2c31188e949a2c40a23a9ffe1a8a8","tid":186780,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d女仔邊到搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公園"},{"pid":"c90482a3528646312f4caeae4b4d6a4bcf8cc7eb","tid":186780,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:47:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d女仔邊到搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俄羅斯"},{"pid":"15ecc0f0e85c0e5b329953eccb7b9b6dbe0c4ac7","tid":186780,"uid":34759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"擺到明知自己會比人拉 留定後路 做媒強姦 之後再講到好似愛情故事咁 感動個官坐少啲"},{"pid":"4e04ba17a8e496a24b3e6144affff3abae44502c","tid":186780,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d女仔邊到搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俄羅斯公園"},{"pid":"adfc812a8437623219efc898a59031a64f77db7b","tid":186780,"uid":65347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d女仔邊到搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三年前俄羅斯公園"},{"pid":"e3ce5110122173ec0677f28bfc6885d627b2a6cc","tid":186780,"uid":94255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:03:13.000Z","msg":"斯德哥爾摩"},{"pid":"f93f1f38712d2b5184071578c8c68c15ea8674e9","tid":186780,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:04:30.000Z","msg":"大愛左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6e36796cb9eba5a7da1cf16bb4f02ebb65ea16","tid":186780,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d女仔邊到搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三年前俄羅斯公園草叢中"},{"pid":"0e65cf6fc224c42df6e621d3bd26669fb31a0d37","tid":186780,"uid":62842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:32:18.000Z","msg":"強姦變另類式友誼波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bce5d0c9488de43aed94ffb4692ae73f8084d51","tid":186780,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54dcb4ed71861eaf242ebd8b8bcc5df03156010","tid":186780,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"典型斯德哥爾摩候群症"},{"pid":"64a43e49ebcfde0308afcc29fa8ec685a469ae30","tid":186780,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢d女仔邊到搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三年前俄羅斯公園草叢中</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實周街都有，只要你超靚仔/鬼佬"},{"pid":"8c24f4cb8bb47e0f7661d7eba9dcf3a8d2dd41cb","tid":186780,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>典型斯德哥爾摩候群症</blockquote><br />\n我都想講"},{"pid":"321334fdbdda992b11dc38a6b46243bbc6ca4dd8","tid":186780,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:39:50.000Z","msg":"變成你的形狀了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f392e1f3ce9abbc4005542051b636d7b6e8aeb82","tid":186780,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T01:00:17.000Z","msg":"駛左幾錢"}]}